        <Parent_String>radiometers [300201521], radiant energy measuring devices [300200419], elemental forces measuring devices [300195710], measuring devices for forces [300195702], measuring devices (instruments) [300207870], Measuring Devices (hierarchy name) [300207851], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
